Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.62,0:23:40.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:43.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:49.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 还有人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:52.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…没见过的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:57.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:23:59.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:01.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:04.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.68,0:24:06.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你是哪里的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:13.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是没有父母 或者不能和父母一起的孩子来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:15.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.87,0:24:23.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常在一起 保护自己的人…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.73,0:24:27.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.62,0:24:30.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也不是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.90,0:24:34.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎样的爸爸跟妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.36,0:24:38.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是很体贴的人 看着你就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:47.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.43,0:24:50.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很可怕的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.33,0:25:00.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.27,0:25:01.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.39,0:25:02.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.66,0:25:04.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.48,0:25:06.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么可怕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.53,0:25:16.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也挺辛苦的呀
